</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>美國實驗老鼠成功「返老還童」 研究指長期施用山中因子可逆轉衰老</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/12/cellular-rejuvenation-therapy-safely-reverses-signs-of-aging-in-mice/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=cellular-rejuvenation-therapy-safely-reverses-signs-of-aging-in-mice</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 12 Mar 2022 07:16:00 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[山中因子]]></category><category><![CDATA[返老還童]]></category><category><![CDATA[逆齡]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1090000</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>每個人都會隨著年歲漸漸老去，可能是頭頂的髮絲開始變白，可能是記憶力開始下降，這些都是衰老的跡象。但如果有機會可 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">每個人都會隨著年歲漸漸老去，可能是頭頂的髮絲開始變白，可能是記憶力開始下降，這些都是衰老的跡象。但如果有機會可以逆轉衰老，你又會想嘗試返老還童嗎？美國早前有研究報告指出，科學家成功對實驗鼠實施細胞再生療法，重置了老鼠肉體的年齡，真正實現「逆齡」。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1090001" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/848E047A-FCB1-4501-88E8-E03803805AB5-694x383.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="383" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/848E047A-FCB1-4501-88E8-E03803805AB5-694x383.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/848E047A-FCB1-4501-88E8-E03803805AB5-1280x706.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/848E047A-FCB1-4501-88E8-E03803805AB5-768x423.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/848E047A-FCB1-4501-88E8-E03803805AB5-1536x847.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/848E047A-FCB1-4501-88E8-E03803805AB5-2048x1129.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/848E047A-FCB1-4501-88E8-E03803805AB5.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">美國沙克研究所（Salk Institute for Biological Studies）與基因工程科技公司（Genentech）共組的研究團隊，針對不同年齡的實驗用鼠實施「逆齡療法」。較老的老鼠一旦受傷，皮膚細胞的修復能力較差；年老老鼠同時也有更高機率患上癌症或一些退化性神經疾病，自然衰老的表現與人類相似。接受療法的實驗用鼠分別相當於人類年齡的 50-70 歲、35-70 歲及 80 歲以上，結果並未出現神經系統上的衰老退化，更沒有任何一隻老鼠出現癌症。受到逆齡治療的老鼠在心臟、大腦、視神經與肌肉再生等能力上，都有別於自然衰老的對照組，且未被觀察到足以影響安全性的副作用。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1090002" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/F8F682B9-CB69-4894-94BF-71B87845BDDE-694x384.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/F8F682B9-CB69-4894-94BF-71B87845BDDE-694x384.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/F8F682B9-CB69-4894-94BF-71B87845BDDE-1280x708.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/F8F682B9-CB69-4894-94BF-71B87845BDDE-768x425.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/F8F682B9-CB69-4894-94BF-71B87845BDDE-1536x850.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/F8F682B9-CB69-4894-94BF-71B87845BDDE-2048x1133.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/F8F682B9-CB69-4894-94BF-71B87845BDDE.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1090003" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/39CC58DC-AAF3-4801-8E8E-6782ECAEC78A-694x386.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/39CC58DC-AAF3-4801-8E8E-6782ECAEC78A-694x386.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/39CC58DC-AAF3-4801-8E8E-6782ECAEC78A-1280x712.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/39CC58DC-AAF3-4801-8E8E-6782ECAEC78A-768x427.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/39CC58DC-AAF3-4801-8E8E-6782ECAEC78A-1536x855.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/39CC58DC-AAF3-4801-8E8E-6782ECAEC78A-2048x1139.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/39CC58DC-AAF3-4801-8E8E-6782ECAEC78A.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1090004" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/F558D0C3-B855-438E-A35F-357744FD1292-694x382.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="382" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/F558D0C3-B855-438E-A35F-357744FD1292-694x382.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/F558D0C3-B855-438E-A35F-357744FD1292-1280x704.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/F558D0C3-B855-438E-A35F-357744FD1292-768x422.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/F558D0C3-B855-438E-A35F-357744FD1292-1536x845.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/F558D0C3-B855-438E-A35F-357744FD1292-2048x1126.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/F558D0C3-B855-438E-A35F-357744FD1292.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">所謂的逆齡療法其核心在於「山中因子」，即是 Oct4、Sox2、K1f4 和 cMyc。Oct4、Sox2、C-Myc 和 K1f4 能將細胞的表觀遺傳標記重置回原始模式，使已分化的體細胞重編程（reprogramming）為具有類似胚胎幹細胞狀態的「誘導型多潛能幹細胞」（iPS 細胞）。沙克研究所早於 2016 年研究使用山中因子對抗衰老跡象，延長患有早衰症實驗用鼠的壽命。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">研究所科學家 Pradeep Reddy 表示，「我們真正想確認的是，長時間施用山中因子是否安全。的確，我們沒有看到這些動物的健康、行為或體重，有受到任何負面的影響。」；實驗室教授 Juan Carlos 1Zpisua Belmonte 亦指出，「除了解決與老化相關的疾病，這種方法還為生物醫學界提供一種新工具，在不同疾病情況下（例如神經退化性疾病），透過改善細胞功能和韌性，來恢復組織和生物體的健康。」研究團隊正在規劃未來將分析在長期的山中因子治療下，特定分子和基因如何發生變化，同時開發傳遞因子的新方法。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來：<a href="https://www.salk.edu/news-release/cellular-rejuvenation-therapy-safely-reverses-signs-of-aging-in-mice/">Salk Institute</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
